This medically confirmed report was received from a physician via a company representative on 05MAR2015. 
A patient died from pancytopenia while receiving H P Acthar (CORTICOTROPIN) Injection 80 U/ml (additional 
details not reported). The physician was not sure if the death was due to H P Acthar or not. 
Causality
1) Pancytopenia
As Reported: Not Reported 
As Determined: Unevaluable
Company comment:
A patient of unknown age and sex died from pancytopenia while receiving Acthar with unknown dose and frequency
